g.aria-label: Validation mode: trained on synthetic data only
Test mode: trained on synthetic and real data

Datasets 1 to 5 consist of 5000 synthesized image and 516 real one. 1. basic_5516: black text centered on a white image. 2. bg15_5516: black text centered on a background randomly chosen from a set of 15. 3. bg15_s_5516: same as 2 with font size variations. 4. bg15_spi_5516: same as 2 with font size, text position, and color intensity variations. 5. bg48_spi_5516: same as 4 with an extended set of 48 background. 6. bg48_spi_40516: same as 5 with 40,000 synthesized image and 516 real one.
